3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper considers the use of beamforming and user selection strategies to improve the performance of the network, which involves control and optimization techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper mentions the use of multi-antenna relay to assist transmission, which can be related to multimedia applications that require high data rates and reliable transmission. 
5. cs.COM (Computers and Society): Although less likely, the paper may also relate to the societal impact of improving the performance of wireless networks, such as enabling better connectivity and communication for remote and underprivileged areas.
